*Apr. 2024 - Aug. 2024*  

- - -



Research Approach  
===  

- Utilized Unity3D to develop VR game environments, focusing on interactivity, complex scene construction, and narrative-driven puzzle gameplay. 
- Implemented VR interaction systems including animation triggers, user interface (UI) design, and collider triggers to boost interactivity and immersion.
- Ensured smooth VR hardware integration with VR headsets and hand controllers. 



